<%- include("background.ejs") %>

<style>
    /* Page Styling */
    .content-wrapper {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 40px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    /* Heading Section */
    .content-wrapper h1 {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        color: #3a6e2b;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* Section Title */
    .content-wrapper h2 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        color: #2f4507;
        margin-top: 40px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* Paragraph Text */
    .content-wrapper p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #333;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    /* Bullet Points */
    .content-wrapper ul {
        list-style-type: disc;
        padding-left: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    /* List Items */
    .content-wrapper ul li {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
    }

    /* Quote Styling */
    .content-wrapper blockquote {
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        color: #555;
        padding: 20px;
        border-left: 4px solid #3a6e2b;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        margin: 30px 0;
        border-radius: 10px;
    }

    /* Highlighted Text */
    .content-wrapper span.highlight {
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #3a6e2b;
    }

    /* Icon Bullet Points */
    .content-wrapper .icon-list {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .content-wrapper .icon-list li {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .content-wrapper .icon-list li i {
        color: #3a6e2b;
        margin-right: 10px;
    }

    /* Line Break */
    .line-break {
        margin: 30px 0;
        border-top: 2px solid #3a6e2b;
    }

    /* Image and Text Side by Side */
    .content-with-image {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: row; /* Ensures image and text stay side by side */
        gap: 20px;
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .content-with-image img {
        max-width: 40%; /* Set image width smaller for better balance */
        height: auto;
        border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .content-with-image .content-text {
        max-width: 60%; /* Ensure text takes up more space */
        flex-grow: 1;
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .content-with-image {
            flex-direction: column; /* Stacks image and text vertically on smaller screens */
        }

        .content-with-image img,
        .content-with-image .content-text {
            max-width: 100%; /* Full width for both elements on mobile */
        }
    }
</style>

<div class="content-wrapper">
    <h1>Strengthening Civil Society and Community Leadership</h1>

    <!-- Content Section: Building Community Leadership -->
    <div class="content-with-image">
        <img src="todaycom.png" alt="Todcom" />
        <div class="content-text">
            <h2>Building Community Leadership</h2>
            <p>MFH is committed to empowering communities through strategic <span class="highlight">Community Strengthening</span> initiatives, focusing on promoting leadership among men, women, and youth. We aim to cultivate a deep understanding of the vital role Community-Based Organizations (CBOs) and People’s Organizations (POs) play in the development process.</p>
            <ul class="icon-list">
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Training on group management, conflict resolution, and local resource mobilization</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Ensuring access to government schemes, livelihood programs, and health services</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Emphasizing local resource mobilization for long-term financial viability</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <blockquote>"Our goal is to build confidence and self-reliance, allowing communities to operate independently over time." — Mountain Forum Himalayas</blockquote>

    <div class="line-break"></div>

    <!-- Content Section: Empowering Civil Society -->
    <div class="content-with-image">
        <img src="todstr.png" alt="Today str" />
        <div class="content-text">
            <h2>Empowering Civil Society Organizations</h2>
            <p>MFH is dedicated to strengthening the capacity and effectiveness of civil society organizations across the Himalayan region. We achieve this by providing targeted support and resources that enable CSOs to better advocate for their communities, address local issues, and collaborate with other stakeholders.</p>
            <ul class="icon-list">
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Facilitating training workshops and strengthening compliances</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Offering strategic guidance and fostering networking opportunities</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Advocating for social transformation, environmental sustainability, and social justice</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="line-break"></div>

    <p>MFH’s development process is people-centered, context-specific, and grounded in participatory and democratic values. We strive to protect the rights and dignity of the poor, while strengthening the perspectives and capacities of all stakeholders.</p>
</div>

